Create a Spring Boot + Thymeleaf based homepage for a coding platform called "AI Code Explorer".

Requirements:

1. Top navigation bar:
   - Logo text: AI Code Explorer
   - Menu items: Discuss, Interview, Log in, Sign Up

2. Hero section:
   - Title: "Explore Programming Problems"
   - Subtitle: "Browse Java problems by category and find solutions explained in simple language."
   - Search bar to search problems

3. Left sidebar:
   - All Java Problems
   - Array Problems
   - String Problems
   - Dynamic Programming
   - Algorithmic Puzzles

4. Main content area:
   - Show category cards:
       - Array Problems (25 problems)
       - String Problems (30 problems)
       - Dynamic Programming (20 problems)

5. When clicking a category (like Array Problems),
   show list of problems:
       - Reverse an Array
       - Find Maximum Subarray
       - Remove Duplicates
       - Rotate Array

Use clean modern UI with CSS.
Do not use React.
Use only Spring Boot + Thymeleaf + HTML + CSS.